719434f-a.folder: East End Avenue & 81st Street, Manhattan, NY

719435f-b.text:
East End Avenue, north across East 81st Street. To the left is a cleared area extending from 80th to 81st St's. view 2 is limited to the west side, emphasizing the N.W.
corner of East 81st Street.
September 29, 1940
No's. 1-2
P. L. Sperr
